title: Meet and Fuck Games (up to July 5th 2013)
description:
I haven't tried all the games yet, but they all seem to work with the included baka loader.

I didn't crack or pack this thing, i just downloaded it from another site and made a torrent for it. I would love to give credit to whoever made this, but half the site i got it from is in Japanese and i barely managed to find the download link... so i have no idea who deserves the credit for it. Sorry.

I'll just assume he won't mind a little help spreading this a little further (i hope)

Enjoy and Seed a little, please!
